dc_description_s: This point data layer represents Public Land Survey System (PLSS) corners for Florence County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Florence_PLSS_2017. [Data created using field gathered data and information provided through Florence County, Wisconsin Register of Deeds research.Direct Observation points were created from actual survey point data or from coordinates listed on recorded Certified Survey Maps (CSM).Calculated points were established by bearings and distances shown on numerous CSMs when tied to known corner locations.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
